                            <comment id="493440" author="JIRAUSER19288" created="Mon, 20 Apr 2026 08:26:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ddiwang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ddiwang&quot;&gt;ddiwang&lt;/a&gt; !&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="493324" author="JIRAUSER19464" created="Sun, 19 Apr 2026 02:13:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I will fix it in &#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64320&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64320&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="493323" author="JIRAUSER19464" created="Sun, 19 Apr 2026 02:12:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah I accidentally reset some parameter in mdt_tunables_init(), which caused this issue.&#160; I will fix this in &#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64320&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64320&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p&gt;diff --git a/lustre/mdt/mdt_lproc.c b/lustre/mdt/mdt_lproc.c&lt;br/&gt;
index c1071a2f56..728274bdd6 100644&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;#8212; a/lustre/mdt/mdt_lproc.c&lt;br/&gt;
+++ b/lustre/mdt/mdt_lproc.c&lt;br/&gt;
@@ -1664,6 +1664,12 @@ int mdt_tunables_init(struct mdt_device *mdt, const char *name)&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; ENTRY;&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; LASSERT(name != NULL);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+ &#160; &#160; &#160; mdt-&amp;gt;mdt_enable_remote_dir = 1;&lt;br/&gt;
+ &#160; &#160; &#160; mdt-&amp;gt;mdt_enable_remote_dir_gid = -1;&lt;br/&gt;
+ &#160; &#160; &#160; mdt-&amp;gt;mdt_enable_chprojid_gid = -1;&lt;br/&gt;
+ &#160; &#160; &#160; mdt-&amp;gt;mdt_enable_pin_gid = -1;&lt;br/&gt;
+ &#160; &#160; &#160; mdt-&amp;gt;mdt_enable_striped_dir = 1;&lt;br/&gt;
+&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; obd-&amp;gt;obd_ktype.default_groups = KOBJ_ATTR_GROUPS(mdt);&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; obd-&amp;gt;obd_debugfs_vars = ldebugfs_mdt_obd_vars;&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; rc = lprocfs_obd_setup(obd, true);&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Thanks! Marc&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="493129" author="JIRAUSER19288" created="Wed, 15 Apr 2026 09:17:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The first patch in the series that shows the regression is &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19921&quot; title=&quot;Lustre GSS IAM integration&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19921&quot;&gt;LU-19921&lt;/a&gt; target: add target verification | &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64320&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64320&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="493128" author="JIRAUSER19288" created="Wed, 15 Apr 2026 08:45:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Maloo reports a close to 20% failure rate, with failures occurring several times per day since 2026-03-30. It is only affecting &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19921&quot; title=&quot;Lustre GSS IAM integration&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19921&quot;&gt;LU-19921&lt;/a&gt; tickets, so seems to be a regression in that series&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
